ass=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nht1665702561308.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nht1665702561308.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nht1665702561308.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nht1665702561308\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"nht1665702561308__write_249891\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Write the current occurrence to the database.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"nht1665702561308__topic_d79817e1_d79818e1_d79819e1\">\n<div class=\"p\" id=\"nht1665702561308__p_d79820e1_d79821e1_d79822e1\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"nht1665702561308__codeblock_jqv_hnz_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">write</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nht1665702561308__topic_d52522e1_d52523e1_d52524e1_d52525e1_d52526e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1012110e65\">Return Values </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span></span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__2\">Data was successfully written. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__1\"> &lt; <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__2\">An error occurred.\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__2\">No entities are painted on the\n                        component.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-3</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__2\">Exceptional I/O error (hardware or software). </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-4</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__2\">Open request for table or file failed. The\n                        table or file is not painted, or it does not exist. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-5</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__2\">Update request for non-updatable\n                        occurrence.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-6</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__2\">Exceptional I/O error on write request; for\n                        example, lack of disk space, no write permission, or violation of a database\n                        constraint. Check the message frame for details.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-7</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__2\"> Duplicate key.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-10</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__2\">Occurrence has been modified or removed since\n                        it was retrieved; the occurrence should be reloaded.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-11</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__2\">Occurrence already locked.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-15</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__2\">Uniface network error. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-16</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7889e1_d7890e1_d7891e1__entry__2\">Network error: unknown. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7892e1_d7893e1_d7894e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values commonly returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> following write</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7892e1_d7893e1_d7894e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7892e1_d7893e1_d7894e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7892e1_d7893e1_d7894e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7892e1_d7893e1_d7894e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-2</code>  through  <code class=\"ph codeph\">-12</code></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7892e1_d7893e1_d7894e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UIOSERR_*&gt;</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7892e1_d7893e1_d7894e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">Errors during database\n                        I/O.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7892e1_d7893e1_d7894e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-16</code>  through  <code class=\"ph codeph\">-30</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7892e1_d7893e1_d7894e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UNETERR_*&gt;</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7892e1_d7893e1_d7894e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">Errors during network I/O.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7892e1_d7893e1_d7894e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7892e1_d7893e1_d7894e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UGENERR_ERROR&gt;</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nht1665702561308__table_d7892e1_d7893e1_d7894e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> An error occurred. No entities\n                        are painted on the component.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nht1665702561308__topic_d52527e1_d52528e1_d52529e1_d52530e1_d52531e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1012110e322\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nht1665702561308__p_d79829e1_d79830e1_d79831e1\">Allowed in all component types except Reports.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nht1665702561308__topic_d52532e1_d52533e1_d52534e1_d52535e1_d52536e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1012110e331\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nht1665702561308__p_d79835e1_d79836e1_d79837e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">write</span> statement writes an\n            occurrence to the database. This statement should only be used in the write or writeUp\n            triggers. If fields of the occurrences have ProcScript in their formatToDbms trigger,\n            the formatToDbms triggers are activated.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nht1665702561308__section_vh3_jwq_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1012110e344\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">write</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example uses the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">write</span> statement in\n               the write trigger to log information about which user updated or created a particular\n               occurrence.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104nht1665702561308_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"nht1665702561308__codeblock_xyg_jnz_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger write\n if ($dbocc = 0)\n CREATED_BY = $user\n CREATED_DATE = $date\n else\n UPDATED_BY = $user\n endif\n write\nend; write</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vvq1665702552959.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>read</a><p>Set the access mode.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kgi1665702560769.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>store</a><p>Initiate validation and storage of all occurrences marked as modified. It activates the appropriate validation triggers as required, followed by the write and delete triggers.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rog1665702561386.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger writeUp</a><p>System trigger that handles processing when a new or modified occurrence of an Up entity must be written to the database.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530258\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530258\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "write Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Write the current occurrence to the database. write Copy Return Values Table 1. Values returned in $status Value Meaning 0 Data was successfully written. < 0 An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. -1 No entities are painted on the component. -3 Exceptional I/O error (hardware or software). -4 Open request for table or file failed. The table or file is not painted, or it does not exist. -5 Update request for non-updatable occurrence. -6 Exceptional I/O error on write request; for example, lack of disk space, no write permission, or violation of a database constraint. Check the message frame for details. -7 Duplicate key. -10 Occurrence has been modified or removed since it was retrieved; the occurrence should be reloaded. -11 Occurrence already locked. -15 Uniface network error. -16 Network error: unknown. Table 2. Values commonly returned by $procerror following write Value Error constant Meaning -2 through -12 <UIOSERR_*> Errors during database I/O. -16 through -30 <UNETERR_*> Errors during network I/O. -1 <UGENERR_ERROR> An error occurred. No entities are painted on the component. Use Allowed in all component types except Reports. Description The write statement writes an occurrence to the database. This statement should only be used in the write or writeUp triggers. If fields of the occurrences have ProcScript in their formatToDbms trigger, the formatToDbms triggers are activated. Example: Using write The following example uses the write statement in the write trigger to log information about which user updated or created a particular occurrence. Explain this code trigger write if ($dbocc = 0) CREATED_BY = $user CREATED_DATE = $date else UPDATED_BY = $user endif write end; write Copy Related Links read Set the access mode. store Initiate validation and storage of all occurrences marked as modified. It activates the appropriate validation triggers as required, followed by the write and delete triggers. trigger writeUp System trigger that handles processing when a new or modified occurrence of an Up entity must be written to the database. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}